title: I Love the Ocean
content:
I love the ocean. I always have.

But sometimes I wonder… do I have to drown to prove it?
I don’t want to disappear in what I love. I just want to feel it, let it move me, let it stay a part of me without taking me apart.

Some love asks too much. True love? True love lets you breathe.
